ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[This undiagnosed illness seems to be spreading and seems to be affecting
young people more than older individuals. The symptoms presented in this
article do not jump out at me as having any specific disease association.
I am interested in the results of a toxic panel screen. There is indication
in the article that a tox screen has been run, but no results are included.
We would be interested in these results as well as the results of any other
tests. - Mod.TG]
